業既...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為個個都心諗，我做足100分負責任地拎萬幾蚊<br />\n個樓價不負責任地升到兩萬蚊呎<br />\n邊個答我負責任呀？"},{"pid":"ad1c2b8c6444b1e3f136e421e68b751b0455bb35","tid":195500,"uid":987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:31:42.000Z","msg":"做咁好做咩呀，博升呀"},{"pid":"920f7b421ad7ee47a077dde4524bf79259730dd3","tid":195500,"uid":64858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:41:35.000Z","msg":"港鐵買大陸車你賴人做野唔認真？<br />\n樓豬你食撚左屎？"},{"pid":"12bd433b0e5da992297311c724be6842c68a747a","tid":195500,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T16:56:29.000Z","msg":"大公司，少做少錯，按程序做就夠晒啦。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n做得多無獎架"},{"pid":"b8db62f0b4a7bc725dc4b85671cbb6e65864fd35","tid":195500,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:00:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港鐵買大陸車你賴人做野唔認真？<br />\n樓豬你食撚左屎？</blockquote><br />\n乜都開個post踩香港人先"},{"pid":"96ee318807edacdf01e4b88202c606164ed4d7f1","tid":195500,"uid":24572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:21:05.000Z","msg":"其實唔係屌緊保養維修果班前綫，<br />\n係d 高層，落決定果班。<br />\n包括決定買大陸野果班。"},{"pid":"42e0e48a17f7a90cc41a32fa13e7f817c16c04a5","tid":195500,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:36:50.000Z","msg":"係香港落手落腳做野果班前線真係好撚慘<br />\n人工低工時長社會地位低<br />\n寫字樓嘆冷氣unun腳就袋你幾倍人工"},{"pid":"29969bc6ab6865a467e29a84de02628aac99d1df","tid":195500,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:36:54.000Z","msg":"人工低冇福利<br />\n咁博做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個心態咪 返工等放工"},{"pid":"9895a2f17cd2c83659cff5a6dcf5352c87a8b2de","tid":195500,"uid":14337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港落手落腳做野果班前線真係好撚慘<br />\n人工低工時長社會地位低<br />\n寫字樓嘆冷氣unun腳就袋你幾倍人工</blockquote><br />\nAgger"},{"pid":"9c87746cc